edu.cnm.deepdive.heydoc.models

Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.heydoc.models.Account

  • public class Account
extends Object
    The Account class is used for the users account information. It displays the lastname, firstname of the user, and displays whether they have a scheduled appointment or if they recently cancelled any. In the floating action button it displays the users basic health statistics
